short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Jump to and back from a specified Desmos screen, potentially with notes on it.  Unoffical release.  Created by David Chachere.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Jump to and back from a user specified Desmos screen, potentially with notes on it.  Three additional navigation buttons are added to all Desmos Activity screens in the student view.  One is for setting and resetting the screen with notes on it, another is for jumping to the screen with the notes, and the third is for returning back to the screen left before jumping to the notes.  This is an unofficial Chrome extension for Desmos created by David Chachere.
